title: Converse Rubber Tracks London - Studio Trick #1 Feedback with Crows
description:
Converse Rubber Tracks London opened it's studio doors in Haringey this week, inviting psychedelic-garage band Crows to record for the day. Guitarist Steve took time out of his session to show us a cool trick to get the exact feedback you want.
